The Berserk state has several disadvantages, however: They attack the nearest creature until that creature is dead, then moving on to the next target. The Hit Points of the imbiber are masked for the duration of the effect, and the imbiber cannot benefit from any effect that heals Hit Points. At the end of the potion's duration, the imbiber becomes fatigued and <PRO_HISHER> Strength drops to 3 for 2 turns.

