//Phantom Blade
@40350 = ~Oil of Phantom Blade~
@40351 = ~When poured, this oil forms into a translucent, shadow-like, weightless area of magical force extending from the applicant's hand. The silent, blade-shaped construct's cutting edges inflict damage just as those of a real sword do. This sword can only be used by the applicant and remains in <PRO_HISHER> hand for the duration or until dispelled.

The phantom blade acts as a +3 magical sword in terms of to-hit and damage bonuses as well as the type of creatures it can hit. However, due to its etheric nature, it causes an extra +10 damage against undead creatures.

