Duration: %num_rounds% rounds

Weight: 1~


//Minor Spell Turning
@40352 = ~Oil of Minor Spell Turning~
@40353 = ~This oil causes the spells cast against the applicant to rebound upon the original caster. This affects a total of 4 spell levels, including spells cast from scrolls and innate spell-like abilities.

This effect excludes the following: area effects that are not centered directly upon the applicant, as well as area effects that are stationary, such as Cloudkill and Stinking Cloud. As long as the spell is cast directly at the applicant, it will be reflected back upon the caster. This spell will only affect up to 4th-level spells, but as long as there are levels remaining, a spell will be reflected. For example, if there is only 1 level left and a 3rd-level spell is cast at the wizard, the spell will be reflected while canceling the Spell Turning.

This spell will not protect the applicant from Dispel Magic, but will not be dispelled by Dispel Magic either.

STATISTICS:

Special: Reflects up to 4 levels worth of spells back at original caster
Duration: %num_rounds% rounds

Weight: 1~


//Heal
@40354 = ~Tonic of Heal~
@40355 = ~This tonic wipes away disease and injury in the imbiber. It completely cures all disease and blindness and heals all points of damage suffered due to wounds or injury. It also dispels a Feeblemind spell and cures those mental disorders caused by spells or injury to the brain. Naturally, the effects can be negated by later wounds, injuries, and diseases.

STATISTICS:

