//Entropy Shield
@40358 = ~Extract of Entropy Shield~
@40359 = ~This oil surrounds the applicant with a defensive maelstrom of energy that blocks or deflects many attacks. This gives the applicant a +6 bonus to Armor Class, a +2 bonus to Saving Throws, and +50% resistance to electricity, fire, cold, and acid. The applicant is also immune to Flamestrike and all missile-based attacks, including missiles created by spells such as Magic Missile.

