//Spell Trap
@40390 = ~Draught of Spell Trap~
@40391 = ~This concotion creates a barrier of magical protection around the imbiber. Every spell that hits the barrier is absorbed by the power of the spell trap —— making the imbiber recall a previously cast spell. The spell trap provides 30 levels of protection (i.e., ten Flame Arrows or five Fingers of Death). The spell trap can absorb any level of spell, from one to nine.

For example, if a wizard shields <PRO_HIMHER>self with Spell Trap and is then hit by a Flame Arrow (3rd-level spell), <PRO_HESHE> gets three spell levels back—<PRO_HESHE> will regain one spell up to 3rd level in power.

