//Improved Alacrity
@40394 = ~Philter of Improved Alacrity~
@40395 = ~This concotion essentially erases the pause between casting spells. When cast, the imbiber can begin casting a new spell the instant <PRO_HESHE> is finished casting <PRO_HISHER> current spell. The effect lasts for 2 rounds.

